! conclusion: The current distortions in identity-space project into PCE-space as [🔥/亏 🌹/门]
              systemic misalignments that threaten research culture if unaddressed.

  + THEN: Operate an explicit move on the named axis (see substructure below); steward the pattern against the declared discipline.

Career development and professional growth are hindered by the
                   repository’s operational design.

If left unchecked, the current projection of identity distortions into
                 PCE space results in a viable-system failure: reduced sustainability,
                 weakened integrity, fragmented connectivity, compromised inclusivity,
                 and stunted development.

  + because: Strategy becomes reactive rather than robust.

  + because: Responsibility is inconsistently expressed across the system.

  + because: Connectivity becomes siloed and brittle.

  + because: Inclusivity is reduced to aspiration rather than practice.

  + because: Development pathways are constrained by system friction.
